summary: Thijs Launspach, MSc (1988) is a Dutch psychologist and teacher at The School of Life. He has written extensively about mental health (especially among adolescents), about stress and the pressure to perform. Among his books are the bestsellers Crazy Busy (2018), You Are Enough (2022) and Managing Millennials (2019). Thijs is a regular speaker, podcaster and has a weekly column in the Algemeen Dagblad, the biggest newspaper in the Netherlands.
